{"tid":161090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「開埋吹水台」有冇人覺得香港文化慢慢復燃緊？","createTime":"2017-03-18T09:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T13:06:11.000Z","uid":23863,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"402f0e493e8537130b5dfb50102023e9d60992c5","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是咁的，最近我同我嘅朋友搞咗一個目前仲係好細嘅平台，希望用影片形式（姐係Youtube同Facebook) 去講下唔同嘅香港文化同香港嘅狀況。 咁樣做嘅原因，其實係想向內同向外講下香港嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n我地依家有嘅問題，除咗係整片上嘅技術，就係我地做到嘅題目同內容唔夠多同闊。我地需要更多嘅創作者去擴闊個平台嘅涵蓋範圍，從而再吸引多啲唔同嘅觀眾一齊去了解下香港嘅文化其實係有幾咁豐富。<br />\n<br />\n如果你有興趣參與我地，大家可以入去呢個Telegram Group，歡迎大家喺入面了解多啲 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAzVZtXGqfbrx-tA8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAzVZtXGqfbrx-tA8w&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ee45b669\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAzVZtXGqfbrx-tA8w</a><br />\n<br />\n另外呢個係我地Facebook Page，入面會有我地呢個平台嘅簡介：<a href=\"https://web.facebook.com/happykongner/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.facebook.com%2Fhappykongner%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=eec96e44\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.facebook.com/happykongner/?fref=ts</a><br />\n<br />\n希望可以有更多嘅香港人加入我地，一齊去為我地嘅文化做多少少嘅付出。    <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec8bd3b3d9e293da5f3961e59e741dbc9491639","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推，邊個偷偷留下負評。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d468402a59f789e4643079483749f842c07e7d8","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"深深一推"},{"pid":"668a1b11407a97d1538a4119c965dfd8748d4001","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:33:06.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊推"},{"pid":"c9ba43139fe99b886f419cfd4c7e9b85576deac7","tid":161090,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深深一推</blockquote><br />\n又講咸嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f8c59bb25b5b94c3b54d6fc1909a320993e9ba","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>深深一推</blockquote><br />\n又講咸嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n推深啲"},{"pid":"86ec341c74a0135f944de35517cb800678764ccb","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"食飯前一推"},{"pid":"e872710e3f7362a5ea08dc1cceeda2b2ccc22000","tid":161090,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"斷你10連"},{"pid":"d56a7bd5499f45b175e6f52e66b01095e75875ad","tid":161090,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔覺<img src=\"/asse