03-18T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如你又同我講下點樣復燃緊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多咗人留意香港或者so call本土文化。<br />\n<br />\n不如你又講下有幾天真。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普教中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我地反擊嘅原因。<br />\n<br />\n何來天真？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係話香港冇人珍惜自己嘅文化<br />\n而係絕對稱唔上「復燃」，只係吊緊命咋"},{"pid":"cb1235e0d1487c50727dfee7b18702a1902699ec","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人<br />\n大部分好容易就俾媒體潛移默化<br />\n一定堅持都冇<br />\n學咩人講文化<br />\n媒體講小三，黑材料，優化<br />\n有邊個字唔係已經攻入咗香港文化<br />\n喺連登你仲可以「乜撚小三？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n返到去現實你咁講人哋反而覺得你有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁所以我地咪俾個平台想屌返佢地轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覆埋你下面個comment<br />\n<br />\n唔可以話你錯，但由我見到有人入telegram group，我已經係覺得復燃嘅一種。<br />\n<br />\nJoin us."},{"pid":"9951c7ad456aa8be2003a961b145b684b3b117f9","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ff7b8a9156825561cf136d2dcad47780bf8352","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"b84819e323231d958b969fdda624071495602e7f","tid":161090,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"睡前一推"}]}